<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 06:10:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据报道，哈马斯正在考虑提议，以色列对加沙中部和南部发动袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-29/ty-article-live/report-hamas-official-says-no-major-issues-with-current-cease-fire-poposal/0000018f-27a7-dc45-a78f-3fefefe70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡与拜登通电话，讨论拉法入侵事件 ■ 医学消息人士称，加沙拉法的空袭造成 19 人死亡 ■ 布林肯在以色列访问前抵达沙特阿拉伯 ■ 以色列国防军发言人表示，未来几天将增加进入加沙的人道主义援助</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 02:50:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-29/ty-article-live/report-hamas-official-says-no-major-issues-with-current-cease-fire-poposal/0000018f-27a7-dc45-a78f-3fefefe70000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡、加兰特和以色列国防军主席因加沙战争罪面临国际刑事法院逮捕令，以色列陷入困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-scrambles-as-netanyahu-defense-chiefs-face-possible-icc-arrest-warrants/0000018f-2537-d0a5-abcf-37ff394f0000</link><description>本周可能会对内塔尼亚胡、国防部长约夫·加兰特和陆军参谋长赫兹尔·哈勒维发出逮捕令。一些法律专家表示，司法部长和军队律师应对以色列违反国际法的行为负有部分责任。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 20:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-scrambles-as-netanyahu-defense-chiefs-face-possible-icc-arrest-warrants/0000018f-2537-d0a5-abcf-37ff394f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部发现两名失踪的阿拉伯以色列人的骨头</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/bones-of-two-missing-arab-israelis-found-in-northern-israel/0000018f-25b8-d0a5-abcf-37f8f9cc0000</link><description>两人与阿布·拉蒂夫犯罪组织有联系，警方表示，他们正在探索此案的所有途径，包括犯罪分子之间的不和导致双重谋杀的可能性</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 17:36:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/bones-of-two-missing-arab-israelis-found-in-northern-israel/0000018f-25b8-d0a5-abcf-37f8f9cc0000</guid></item><item><title>国防部长加兰特签署对五名以色列定居者的行政逮捕令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/gallant-signs-administrative-arrest-warrants-against-five-israeli-settlers/0000018f-2539-d0a5-abcf-37f972bc0000</link><description>一名国防官员表示，这五人在本月早些时候针对约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的袭击中发挥了核心作用。国家安全部长本-格维尔批评了这次逮捕行动，称其为“格兰特对定居者的迫害”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 16:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/gallant-signs-administrative-arrest-warrants-against-five-israeli-settlers/0000018f-2539-d0a5-abcf-37f972bc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 205 天：WCK 宣布恢复在加沙的运营</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-205-wck-announces-it-is-resuming-operations-in-gaza/0000018f-2584-d1f3-afcf-2fe54f100001</link><description>由哈利勒·哈亚率领的哈马斯代表团将于周一抵达开罗，与埃及情报官员进行停战谈判 ■ 甘茨称人质归还取代拉法行动 ■ WH：以色列同意在拉法进攻之前听取美国的担忧 ■ 世界中央厨房宣布恢复加沙行动 ■ 战争进入 205 天后您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 16:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-205-wck-announces-it-is-resuming-operations-in-gaza/0000018f-2584-d1f3-afcf-2fe54f100001</guid></item><item><title>不，以色列并不孤单，所以让我们放弃“铁墙”的想法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/no-israel-isnt-alone-so-lets-drop-the-iron-wall-thinking/0000018f-252a-dc45-a78f-3f6b617c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 16:30:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/no-israel-isnt-alone-so-lets-drop-the-iron-wall-thinking/0000018f-252a-dc45-a78f-3f6b617c0000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨表示，如果政府成员阻止人质交易，政府就无权存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/gantz-says-govt-has-no-right-to-exist-if-its-members-prevent-a-hostage-deal/0000018f-253c-d502-a5bf-e5fe6f170000</link><description>甘茨发表此番言论之前，财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇此前曾发表评论，指责内塔尼亚胡允许哈马斯在二十年里变得更加强大，并补充说，同意新的人质交易提案将是“耻辱的投降”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 16:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/gantz-says-govt-has-no-right-to-exist-if-its-members-prevent-a-hostage-deal/0000018f-253c-d502-a5bf-e5fe6f170000</guid></item><item><title>活动人士称，加沙援助船队在船只旗帜被移除后停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/gaza-aid-flotilla-halted-after-vessels-flag-removed-activists-say/0000018f-2553-d1f3-afcf-2f73993e0000</link><description>该船队将于周五从土耳其港口起航，船上载有超过 5,000 吨援助物资。活动人士称几内亚比绍当局的检查和要求是不寻常的和政治性的</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 15:40:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/gaza-aid-flotilla-halted-after-vessels-flag-removed-activists-say/0000018f-2553-d1f3-afcf-2f73993e0000</guid></item><item><title>谢丽尔·桑德伯格的电影为以色列哈马斯性暴力受害者发声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/sheryl-sandbergs-film-gives-voice-to-israeli-victims-of-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018f-2481-d502-a5bf-e4e7d8800000</link><description>在纽约举行的《沉默前的尖叫》首映式上，这位前 Meta 高管表示，这部纪录片将有助于消除人们对哈马斯大规模实施性暴力的否认。该片导演阿纳特·斯大林斯基表示：“以色列不是一个经历过创伤的国家，而是一个处于创伤后阶段的国家。”它正在经历持续的创伤”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 15:27:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/sheryl-sandbergs-film-gives-voice-to-israeli-victims-of-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018f-2481-d502-a5bf-e4e7d8800000</guid></item><item><title>拉法不是加沙的斯大林格勒。这是内塔尼亚胡的又一次操纵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/rafah-is-not-gazas-stalingrad-its-another-manipulation-by-netanyahu/0000018f-2496-d0a5-abcf-37fe560b0000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登的计划可能会真正改变加沙和中东的游戏规则 — — 而且现在比去年更加可行。但当本杰明·内塔尼亚胡仍在以色列发号施令时就不会了</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 15:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/rafah-is-not-gazas-stalingrad-its-another-manipulation-by-netanyahu/0000018f-2496-d0a5-abcf-37fe560b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列球迷因穿着反本格维尔衬衫而被拒绝观看比赛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soccer-fan-denied-access-to-game-for-wearing-anti-ben-gvir-shirt/0000018f-24de-dc45-a78f-3edf07650000</link><description>罗伊·巴尔坎 (Roi Barkan) 和一位朋友表示，他们被禁止观看特拉维夫的一场足球比赛，因为他们穿着写有“FCK BNGVR”的衬衫。警方还获取了他们的个人信息</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 14:17:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soccer-fan-denied-access-to-game-for-wearing-anti-ben-gvir-shirt/0000018f-24de-dc45-a78f-3edf07650000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦总统表示只有美国才能制止以色列对拉法的袭击，预计几天之内</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/palestinian-president-says-only-u-s-can-halt-israels-attack-on-rafah-expected-in-days/0000018f-242d-d1f3-afcf-2f6d678c0000</link><description>马哈茂德·阿巴斯在利雅得举行的世界经济论坛特别会议上发表讲话，呼吁美国“要求以色列不要继续发动袭击”，他认为这可能会导致“巴勒斯坦人民历史上最大的灾难”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 10:55:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/palestinian-president-says-only-u-s-can-halt-israels-attack-on-rafah-expected-in-days/0000018f-242d-d1f3-afcf-2f6d678c0000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家发现墓地可能与古代以色列人有关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-04-28/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-find-cemetery-possibly-linked-to-the-ancient-israelites/0000018f-2344-dacd-a7ef-37c510fb0000</link><description>考古学家称，位于耶斯列山谷的 Horvat Tevet 墓地是罕见的发现，是迦南城邦末期和 3000 多年前圣经以色列王国诞生时期的罕见发现</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 07:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-04-28/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-find-cemetery-possibly-linked-to-the-ancient-israelites/0000018f-2344-dacd-a7ef-37c510fb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列令人垂涎的拉法行动是战略目标还是讨价还价的筹码？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/is-israels-coveted-rafah-operation-a-strategic-target-or-a-bargaining-chip/0000018f-2160-dacd-a7ef-37e1dd300000</link><description>对于埃及来说，结束战争与哈马斯一样至关重要，而拉法行动的准备工作可能会加剧人道主义危机，使埃及与以色列的关系紧张，并导致大量加沙人越过边境，这使得埃及调解人 利害关系方</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 03:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/is-israels-coveted-rafah-operation-a-strategic-target-or-a-bargaining-chip/0000018f-2160-dacd-a7ef-37e1dd300000</guid></item><item><title>人们对哈马斯人质协议寄予厚望，但我们以前见过这种情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/hopes-are-high-for-a-hamas-hostage-deal-but-weve-seen-this-before/0000018f-2116-d0a5-abcf-37fe65380000</link><description>埃及对新一轮谈判的预测是乐观的，但以色列极右翼部长和哈马斯都可能构成不可逾越的障碍。虽然内塔尼亚胡担心国际刑事法院检察官，但如果未达成协议，甘茨和艾森科特退出政府的可能性越来越大</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 03:00:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article/.premium/hopes-are-high-for-a-hamas-hostage-deal-but-weve-seen-this-before/0000018f-2116-d0a5-abcf-37fe65380000</guid></item><item><title>报告：哈马斯官员表示当前停火协议没有“重大”问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article-live/idf-says-26-launches-to-meron-area-in-israels-north-fell-in-open-territories/0000018f-2258-dacd-a7ef-37d9f4ca0000</link><description>在人质谈判中，内塔尼亚胡和拜登通电话，讨论拉法入侵事件 ■ 以色列国防军发言人：未来几天进入加沙的人道主义援助数量将增加 ■ 活动人士称，加沙援助船队在船只旗帜被移除后停止了 ■ 世界中央厨房宣布恢复加沙作战行动 ■ 战时内阁部长甘茨表示，如果阻止人质交易，政府就没有存在的权利</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 01:54:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-28/ty-article-live/idf-says-26-launches-to-meron-area-in-israels-north-fell-in-open-territories/0000018f-2258-dacd-a7ef-37d9f4ca0000</guid></item><item><title>从以色列监狱释放的巴勒斯坦人描述殴打、性虐待和酷刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinian-released-from-israeli-prison-describes-beatings-sexual-abuse-and-torture/0000018f-15e9-d2e1-a7df-15efb6590000</link><description>阿梅尔·阿布·哈利勒 (Amer Abu Halil) 是约旦河西岸居民，曾活跃于哈马斯，未经审判就被监禁，他回忆起他在以色列凯齐奥特监狱经历的战时日常生活</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 21:05:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinian-released-from-israeli-prison-describes-beatings-sexual-abuse-and-torture/0000018f-15e9-d2e1-a7df-15efb6590000</guid></item><item><title>加沙谈判消息来源：哈马斯提供了可行的以色列人质人数，表明积极的转变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/source-in-gaza-talks-hamas-presenting-feasible-hostage-numbers-indicating-positive-shift/0000018f-2116-d1f3-afcf-2b778bbc0000</link><description>消息人士称，作为一种谈判策略，哈马斯一直在夸大其能够运送人质的数量，这有望表明其愿意推动达成协议。一名外交官员表示，以色列尚未同意停止战斗或从加沙撤军</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 20:09:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/source-in-gaza-talks-hamas-presenting-feasible-hostage-numbers-indicating-positive-shift/0000018f-2116-d1f3-afcf-2b778bbc0000</guid></item><item><title>这些抗议人道主义援助的以色列人现在把目光投向了解决加沙问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/these-israelis-protesting-humanitarian-aid-now-have-their-sights-set-on-settling-gaza/0000018f-207d-d1f3-afcf-2b7da58b0000</link><description>几个月来，极右宗教犹太复国主义活动人士一直在监视以色列加沙边境地区，准备突破围栏，进入加沙，并最终重建犹太人定居点。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 18:44:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/these-israelis-protesting-humanitarian-aid-now-have-their-sights-set-on-settling-gaza/0000018f-207d-d1f3-afcf-2b7da58b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议执政联盟，要求达成人质协议；七人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-government-demand-hostage-deal/0000018f-2059-d0a5-abcf-37f966dc0000</link><description>一名被扣押在加沙的人质的母亲说：“哈马斯和[以色列]政府的心越来越硬，政府正在对我发起一场运动”，而以色列所有主要城市都在发生示威活动。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 18:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-27/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-government-demand-hostage-deal/0000018f-2059-d0a5-abcf-37f966dc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>